name: MOO DENG
description: Moodeng is a community-driven meme coin on Ethereum, inspired by a famous hippo from a Thai zoo. MOODENG is a revolutionary project that combines memes, emotional intelligence, and decentralized finance to create a unique and engaging experience. By leveraging the power of memes, MOODENG aims to promote emotional awareness, support mental well-being, and foster a sense of community among its users. At its core, MOODENG is a meme-based platform that utilizes blockchain technology to create a decentralized emotional intelligence network. Users can create, share, and engage with memes that represent various emotions and mental states, such as happiness, sadness, or motivation.
